file.name: swagger-scrape.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:

  version: 1.0.0
  description: |

paths: {}
components:

            countriesSupported:

            installUrl:

            applicationCategory:

            countriesNotSupported:

              type: object
